You were born with potential. You were born with goodness and trust. You were born with ideals. You were born with wings  so learn to use them and fly!
God and men are like 2 lovers who have made a mistake on the location of their meeting place. Men waits for God in time and God waits for men in eternity.
The happiness of ur life depends upon the quality of ur thoughts so guard accordingly and take care that u entertain no notions unsuitable to virtue.
Take time to think  its a source of power. Take time to love and be loved  its a God-given privilege. Take time to work  its the price of success.
Be more concerned with ur character than with ur reputation. Ur character is what u really are while your reputation is merely what others think u are.
Dont be afraid to fail or waste energy trying to cover up for it. Learn from it and go on to the next challenge. Its OK to fail. It helps you grow!
Life should be measured not by the number of years but rather by the love shared  the memories made  the joy given and the blessings received.
You can have anything u want if you want it desperately enough. U must want it with an inner exuberance that erupts through the skin and joins the energy.
As a single footstep will not make a path on the earth so a single thought will not make a pathway in the mind. So we must think over and over again.
Life isnt about expecting and hoping  its about doing and becoming.Its about the choices uve made and the ones ure about to make.Pick wisely!
Life is a great travel trip. The only problem is that it doesnt come with a map.We have to search for our own way to reach the destination.
Its not the strongest of species that survives  nor the most intelligent but the one most responsive to change. Change is the rule of life!
Its always best to be a part of the team who has the same goal rather than belonging to a group that has no perspective on achieving success
Always enjoy life  no matter how hard it seems. When life give you a thousand reasons to cry  show the world that you have million reasons to smile.
Its a good idea to leave your problems to God  but dont complain if they dont get resolved. For u know  its only YOU who can solve them.
A leaf which falls from the tree is at the mercy of wind it goes wherever wind takes it. Be the wind to drive others not the leaf to be driven by others
Integrity is 1 of many paths; it distinguishes itself from the rest  as its the right path and the only one upon which youll never get lost.
Guard ur roving thoughts with a jealous care for speech is but the dialer of thoughts and any1 can plainly read in ur words whats on ur mind.
We live in deeds  not years; in thoughts  not breaths; in feelings  not figures. He lives best  who thinks most  feels the noblest and acts the best.
Friendship is a prized gift that gives our heart a lift  a blessing we just cant do without because friendship is what living is all about!
Every lucky happening and every lucky break are little gifts from God above that are ours to freely take.Always remember God is there for u.
Dreamers are the architects of greatness. Their wisdom lies within their souls.Dream long and hard  because someday your dream will come true.
The poet does not fear death not coz he believes in the fantasy but coz death constantly visits his thoughts and is thus an image of a serene dialogue.
Dont place ur mistakes on ur head  their weight may crush u. Instead place them under ur feet and use them as a platform to view ur horizons.
Dont be like a parrot; be like an eagle.A parrot speaks but cant fly high whereas an eagle is silent and has the willpower to touch the sky!
The only thing weve to fear is fear itself-nameless  unreasoning  unjustified terror which paralyzes needed efforts to convert retreat into advance.
Challenges are tough to those who never face them but easy to those who accept them. Accept every challenge with a smile and see it disappear!
Believe in the rewards that await u  believe in the harvest in store. Believe in the futures promise  each new day gives a new chance to u.
Strength does not come from winning.Your struggles develop your strengths.When you go through hardships and decide not to surrender that is strength.
Being happy doesnt mean everything is perfect  it just means that u decided to look beyond the imperfections. Its a good way to live life.
Appreciation is the highest form of prayer  for it acknowledges the presence of good wherever you shine the light of your thankful thoughts.
Do not spoil what you have by desiring what you do not have; and always remember that what you now have was once among the things you only hoped for.
An optimist is a person who sees a green light everywhere while a pessimist sees only the red stoplight. The truly wise person is colorblind
Always dream and shoot higher than you know how to. Dont bother just to be better than your contemporaries  try to be better than yourself.
Disciplining yourself to do what you know is right and important  although difficult  is the highroad to pride  self-esteem  and personal satisfaction.
A race horse that consistently runs just 1 sec faster than the others is worth millions of dollars more.Never compromise on second position.
Fear less  hope more  eat less  chew more  whine less  breathe more  talk less  say more  hate less  love more and good things will be yours.
Stand upright  speak thy thoughts  declare The truth thou hast  that all may share; Be bold  proclaim it everywhere: They only live who dare.
Circumstances are difficult to change; but by changing yourself  you automatically change the effects of the circumstances and this you can do anytime.
Life has no rewinds and no fast forwards  it unfolds at its own place. So  never miss a chance to live today and make a beautiful story tomorrow.
To wait for someone else  or to expect someone else to make my life richer  or fuller  or more satisfying  puts you in a constant state of suspension.
What matters is to live in the present  live now  for every moment is now. It is your thoughts and acts of the moment that create your future.
Time indeed heals. We just need the minute hand to move on and not let it stop for us to keep going on; without notice the past is far behind.
The most extraordinary thing about this life is that YOU are the author of your own destiny  and you get to decide whats in the next chapter.
You can take from every experience what it has to offer you. And you cannot be defeated if you just keep taking one breath followed by another.
There are some people who live in a dream world  and there are some who face reality and then there are those who turn one into the other.
Real confidence comes from knowing and accepting yourself-your strengths and limitations  in contrast to depending on affirmation from others.
A friend is someone who knows the song in your heart and sings it back to you when you have forgotten how it goes. Be a friend to someone!
What you lost in the past was a part of your destiny  but what you will get in future will be the combination of both your efforts and luck.
Troubles are like washing machines  they twist  turn and knock us around  but in the end we come out cleaner  brighter and better than before.
The game of life is the game of boomerangs. Our thoughts  deeds and words return to us sooner or later. Be kind to get kindness in return.
Strength-Hard work spotlights the character of people: Some turn up their sleeves  some turn up their noses and some dont turn up at all.
One who creates the opportunity is Brilliant. One who gets the opportunity is Lucky. One who capitalizes on the opportunity is the Winner.
If you think youll lose  youll be lost; for out in the world we find success begins with a fellows will; its all in the state of mind!
Past mistakes and failures are like stern and compelling schoolteachers  pushing you to work even harder for great scholarship and success.
